# Allowlist policy: ignore EVERYTHING, then re-admit only our own source and
# documentation.
#
# This folder also holds a 7.8 GB disc image, ~36 GB of extracted game assets
# and several hundred MB of third-party tools. An allowlist means none of that
# can be committed by accident, even by `git add -A`.

*

# --- library, tools, research ---
!nhl2k10/
!nhl2k10/*.py
!nhl2k10/*.md
!research/
!research/*.py
!research/*.md
!ghidra/
!ghidra/*.py
!ghidra/*.java
!ghidra/*.bat
!nhl2k10_gui.py

# --- documentation ---
!docs/
!docs/*.md
!docs/*.csv
!README.md
!LICENSE
!requirements.txt
!.gitignore

# --- game data: never. Bring your own copy. ---
*.iso
*.iso.undo.json
*.xex
*.xma
*.bnk
*.dds
*.wav
extracted/
preview/
2k10*iso*extract*result/
isoextract/

# --- third-party tools: install them yourself ---
ghidra_*_PUBLIC/
jdk/
QuickBMS/
Noesis/
iso2god-*/
20209.3_Xenon_Recovery_with_Symbols/
2K BMS Scripts*/

# --- junk ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
.venv/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
